A

AbstractBufferedFetcher - Class in net.markenwerk.utils.data.fetcher
AbstractBufferedFetcher is a sensible base implementation of Fetcher that uses a byte[] as buffer, to while copying all bytes from an InputStream to an OutputStream by sequentually reading from the InputStream into the buffer and then writing from the buffer to the OutputStream.
